long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
DineSafe is Toronto Public Healthâ€™s food safety program that inspects all establishments serving and preparing food. Each inspection results in a pass, a conditional pass or a closed notice.

This extension uses Open Data from the City of Toronto to look up the latest inspection status for any establishment in Toronto and embeds it directly into your Google search results page. 

DineSafeTO in Google SERPs is not supported by the City of Toronto.
